enrolled-dateline.#text: Begun and held at the City of Washington on Friday, the third day of January, two thousand and fourteen

congress.#text: One Hundred Thirteenth Congress of the United States of America

official-title.#text: Providing a correction in the enrollment of S. 25.

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#tail: shall amend the title so as to read:

text.#text: That in the enrollment of the bill,

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.@value: To ensure that the reduced annual cost-of-living adjustment to the retired pay of members and foreign members of the Armed Forces under the age of 62 required by the Bipartisan Budget Act of 2013 will not apply to members or former members who first became members prior to January 1, 2014, and for other purposes.

role.#text: Clerk of the House of Representatives.
